description:

Besides Q doesn't reveal the real cover ups. I came to the conclusion that this is a psy-op to calm down the people and make them inactive. All I hear is #trusttheplan but I never see anything change, just the nwo moving forward. Ask yourself what is more likely, a government insider dropping intel over 4chan or a psy-op to sedate the freethinkers?
